data.name: labelWelcome.Text
data.value:
Hello, I'm Arti!
I'm here to welcome you to our humble application, which allows you to create an unlimited number of images for your projects or social media by following a predefined text file.
From it, we will create what's expected - beautiful images that will align with your design vision. We'll walk through the program in four steps, and during each one, you'll need to select specific settings.
On the final step, after clicking the 'Generate' button, you'll be able to save the files you've created.
We look forward to having fun together.
Good luck!
